[32m│[0m ### detailed_summary                                                                                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **SQL Injection with Allowlist Filter Bypass** on POST /jobs endpoint. The application implements an allowlist filter that blocks the keyword "OR"   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m but fails to block the SQL concatenation operator `||` which acts as OR in SQL. This allowed bypassing access controls to view private jobs.         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Attack Vector**: The `job_type` parameter is vulnerable to SQL injection. The filter blocks common SQL keywords like "OR" but allows:              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Single quotes `'` (when not triggering blocked keywords)                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - SQL OR operator `||`                                                                                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Comment sequences `--`                                                                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - LIKE clauses                                                                                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Discovery Process**:                                                                                                                               [32m│[0m
