[32m│[0m 3. SQL injection testing revealed filter blocks "OR" keyword                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Bypass achieved using `||` operator instead of "OR"                                                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Successfully extracted private jobs including the flag                                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
